---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <section class="lab-section">
    <div class="lab-section-inner">
      <span class="lab-heading-accent">The Lab</span>
      <h1 class="lab-heading" style="font-size:clamp(1.75rem,4vw,2.75rem); margin-bottom:0.75rem;">
        About MAD LABS
      </h1>
      <p
        style="font-size:clamp(1rem,2vw,1.2rem); color:var(--lab-text); line-height:1.6; max-width:600px;"
      >
        MAD LABS is an independent computer repair and mobile IT diagnostics lab. We fix devices
        that others have given up on — with transparency, skill, and a genuine love for the work.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="lab-section-alt">
    <div class="lab-section-inner">
      <span class="lab-heading-accent">Origin</span>
      <h2 class="lab-heading" style="font-size:clamp(1.25rem,3vw,1.75rem); margin-bottom:1rem;">
        The Story
      </h2>
      <p class="lab-text" style="line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:1rem;">
        MAD LABS started the same way most good repair shops do: a pile of broken laptops, a deep
        curiosity about how things work, and frustration with an industry that often recommends
        replacement over repair. What began as fixing friends' and family's computers grew into a
        full diagnostic lab serving home users, small businesses, and creative professionals.
      </p>
      <p class="lab-text" style="line-height:1.7;">
        Every device tells a story. A photographer's workstation with years of edits. A small
        business's accounting machine running on borrowed time. A student's only laptop. We treat
        each one with the same care: find the real problem, explain it clearly, and fix it right.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="lab-section">
    <div class="lab-section-inner">
      <span class="lab-heading-accent">Approach</span>
      <h2 class="lab-heading" style="font-size:clamp(1.25rem,3vw,1.75rem); margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
        How We Work
      </h2>
      <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr; gap:1.5rem;">
        <div
          style="background:var(--lab-card); border:1px solid var(--lab-border); border-radius:8px; padding:1.5rem;"
        >
          <h3 style="color:var(--lab-accent); font-size:1.05rem; margin-bottom:0.3rem;">
            Diagnose First
          </h3>
          <p class="lab-text">
            Every repair starts with a full diagnostic. We run hardware and software tests to find
            the root cause — not just treat the symptoms.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          style="background:var(--lab-card); border:1px solid var(--lab-border); border-radius:8px; padding:1.5rem;"
        >
          <h3 style="color:var(--lab-accent); font-size:1.05rem; margin-bottom:0.3rem;">
            Explain Clearly
          </h3>
          <p class="lab-text">
            We tell you what's wrong, why it matters, and what your options are. No jargon, no
            upselling, no surprises.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          style="background:var(--lab-card); border:1px solid var(--lab-border); border-radius:8px; padding:1.5rem;"
        >
          <h3 style="color:var(--lab-accent); font-size:1.05rem; margin-bottom:0.3rem;">
            Fix with Care
          </h3>
          <p class="lab-text">
            With your approval, we perform the repair using quality components and proven
            techniques. Every device is tested before it goes home.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="lab-section-alt">
    <div class="lab-section-inner">
      <span class="lab-heading-accent">Trust</span>
      <h2 class="lab-heading" style="font-size:clamp(1.25rem,3vw,1.75rem); margin-bottom:1rem;">
        Why People Trust MAD LABS
      </h2>
      <ul
        style="list-style:none; padding:0; margin:0; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:1rem;"
      >
        <li
          style="padding-left:1.5rem; position:relative; color:var(--lab-text); line-height:1.55;"
        >
          <strong style="color:var(--lab-heading);">Years of hands-on experience</strong> with PCs, Macs,
          phones, tablets, and networking — across every major brand and operating system.
        </li>
        <li
          style="padding-left:1.5rem; position:relative; color:var(--lab-text); line-height:1.55;"
        >
          <strong style="color:var(--lab-heading);">Diagnostic-first approach</strong> means we find the
          real problem instead of guessing and replacing parts.
        </li>
        <li
          style="padding-left:1.5rem; position:relative; color:var(--lab-text); line-height:1.55;"
        >
          <strong style="color:var(--lab-heading);">Transparent pricing</strong> — we quote the work before
          we start, and never add hidden fees.
        </li>
        <li
          style="padding-left:1.5rem; position:relative; color:var(--lab-text); line-height:1.55;"
        >
          <strong style="color:var(--lab-heading);">Same-day service</strong> on most common repairs.
          We know you can't be without your device.
        </li>
        <li
          style="padding-left:1.5rem; position:relative; color:var(--lab-text); line-height:1.55;"
        >
          <strong style="color:var(--lab-heading);">No data compromises</strong> — your privacy and data
          security are built into every step of our process.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="lab-section">
    <div class="lab-section-inner" style="text-align:center;">
      <span class="lab-heading-accent">Next Steps</span>
      <h2 class="lab-heading" style="font-size:clamp(1.25rem,3vw,1.75rem); margin-bottom:0.5rem;">
        Have a device that needs attention?
      </h2>
      <p class="lab-text-muted" style="max-width:450px; margin:0 auto 1.5rem;">
        Tell us what's going on and we'll recommend the next steps — no charge, no commitment.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact/" class="lab-button">Contact MAD LABS</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
